{
  "info": {
    "name": "POS Hono API",
    "_postman_id": "pos-hono-collection",
    "description": "Koleksi Postman buat POS Hono API (Bun + Hono + PostgreSQL). Login pakai JWT access token + refresh token (cookie httpOnly). Habis Login/Register/Refresh, accessToken-nya otomatis kesimpen ke variable koleksi, jadi request lain tinggal pakai {{accessToken}} — nggak usah copy-paste manual.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3000" },
    { "key": "accessToken", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register (cashier)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["v1", "auth", "register"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"kasir.baru@pos.test\",\n  \"password\": \"Rahasia123!\",\n  \"fullName\": \"Kasir Baru\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Daftar user baru. Otomatis jadi role `cashier`. Balikannya accessToken + cookie refresh token (httpOnly) langsung kepasang."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["v1", "auth", "login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@pos.test\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin123!\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Login. Akun buat nyoba: admin@pos.test / Admin123! (admin) atau kasir@pos.test / Kasir123! (kasir). accessToken-nya otomatis kesimpen ke variable koleksi."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (cashier)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["v1", "auth", "login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"kasir@pos.test\",\n  \"password\": \"Kasir123!\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Login sebagai kasir buat ngetes RBAC — coba bikin produk nanti pasti kena 403, soalnya kasir nggak punya izinnya."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/refresh", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["v1", "auth", "refresh"] },
            "description": "Tuker refresh token (dari cookie httpOnly yang diurus Postman otomatis) jadi accessToken baru. Refresh token yang lama langsung dimatiin (rotation)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Me",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/me", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["v1", "auth", "me"] },
            "description": "Ngambil data user dari access token yang lagi aktif."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/logout", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["v1", "auth", "logout"] },
            "description": "Matiin refresh token sama hapus cookie-nya. Balikannya 204 (kosong)."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Products",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List products",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/products?limit=100",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "products"],
              "query": [{ "key": "limit", "value": "100" }]
            },
            "description": "Liat daftar produk. Butuh izin products:read (admin sama kasir dua-duanya punya). limit maksimal 100."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get product by id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/products/p_kopi", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["v1", "products", "p_kopi"] },
            "description": "Ngambil satu produk. Kalau nggak ada, kena 404."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create product (admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/products", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["v1", "products"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"id\": \"p_donat\",\n  \"sku\": \"FD-003\",\n  \"name\": \"Donat Gula\",\n  \"price\": 7000,\n  \"stock\": 40\n}"
            },
            "description": "Bikin produk baru. Butuh izin products:write (cuma admin). Kalau login-nya kasir, bakal kena 403. Harga ditulis dalam rupiah bulat (integer)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update product (admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/products/p_donat", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["v1", "products", "p_donat"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"price\": 8000,\n  \"stock\": 60\n}" },
            "description": "Update sebagian field produk aja. Butuh products:write. Minimal isi satu field."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Checkout",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create checkout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Idempotency-Key", "value": "{{$guid}}", "description": "Wajib diisi. Kalau mau retry, pakai nilai yang sama biar nggak kena charge dobel." }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/v1/checkout", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["v1", "checkout"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"items\": [\n    { \"productId\": \"p_kopi\", \"quantity\": 2 },\n    { \"productId\": \"p_nasi\", \"quantity\": 1 }\n  ],\n  \"discount\": { \"type\": \"percentage\", \"value\": 10 },\n  \"payments\": [\n    { \"method\": \"cash\", \"amount\": 100000 }\n  ]\n}"
            },
            "description": "Proses transaksi jualan. Butuh izin checkout:create. Header Idempotency-Key WAJIB; kalau dikirim ulang pakai key yang sama, dia balikin struk yang sama persis (200, header Idempotent-Replay: true) tanpa bikin transaksi baru. Stok dikurangin secara atomik pakai row lock biar nggak oversell. Diskon opsional (percentage 0-100 atau fixed). PPN 11% dihitung setelah diskon. Total dibulatin ke Rp 100 terdekat. payments boleh lebih dari satu (bayar campur)."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
